In Nimbus framework is using MongoDB with Spring Data.

Integrated with Lister class 
we have a handle class  DefaultMongoModelPersistenceHandler


JavaBeanHandler
It is used to map the properties to Bean while persisting the data.

CURD operation is defined in the Repository class  DefaultMongoModelRepository

MongoDB configuration is done using @Configuration annotations


MongoIdSequenceRepositoryclass used to generate the seq 

The search query is defined in the class
MongoSearchByExample

ParamStateAtomicPersistenceEventListener

 this listener is used to track the task when doing the curd operation 

ParamStateBulkPersistenceEventListener
this listener is used to track the task when doing the bulk operation  

